Flag Debug
  Description: Enable some debug statements.
  Default:     False

Executable gf-tagger
  main-is: gf-tagger.hs
  Other-Modules:
      HagerZhang05
      Context
      Features
  Include-Dirs:
    src
  C-Sources:
    src/cg_descent.c
